thread.title: Australia to expel two Russian diplomats over UK nerve agent attack, hints at World Cup boycott

title: Australia to expel two Russian diplomats over UK nerve agent attack, hints at World Cup boycott
text:
Australia to expel two Russian diplomats over UK nerve agent attack, hints at World Cup boycott 12:51pm IST - 01:15 
Australia plans to expel two Russian diplomats in response to a nerve agent attack on a former Russian spy in the UK and hints at a World Cup boycott. No reporter narration.
